.planning/phases/03-numpress-linear-mz/RESEARCH-port.md:186:This is the authoritative mzPeak file with numpress-linear m/z. We can:
.planning/phases/03-numpress-linear-mz/RESEARCH-port.md:187:1. Read the mzpeak metadata to extract the encoded m/z bytes (from `mz_numpress_linear_bytes` column in `spectra_data.parquet`).
.planning/phases/03-numpress-linear-mz/RESEARCH-port.md:189:3. Compare to the reference m/z (reconstructed from the point layout or schema metadata).
