.planning/phases/03-numpress-linear-mz/RESEARCH-port.md:198:**Question:** Will our C# encodeLinear produce **byte-identical** output to pynumpress / numpress-rs?
.planning/phases/03-numpress-linear-mz/RESEARCH-port.md:200:**Answer:** **YES, within the fixed-point choice.**
