   343	- Full NUnit suite green native arm64 (Phase-1/2 regressions + new MSNumpress + numpress locks).
   344	- mzpeak-validate 0 errors on small.RAW in numpress (default), --lossless, --point.
   345	- L2: decoded numpress m/z within 0.5/fp vs --lossless (anti-vacuity: chunk count > 0, per-chunk length parity, total == spectrum_data_point_count, both anchors); intensity bit-exact f32; --lossless/--point bitwise-L1.
   346	- Numpress correctness: OptimalLinearFixedPoint([1,2,3])==1073741823; reference row-0 fp==10599266.0; byte-identity vs ms-numpress test vector AND vs pynumpress encode at the same fp.
