   371	- Phase 2 (02-01): chunk codec, ChunkFacetStream/ISpectraDataFacet seam, ChunkStructField/ChunkedSpectrumArrayIndex footer, --point/--chunk-size, cv_list registration machinery, MzPeakParquet.NullList. Extend, do not fork.
   372	- Phase 1: streaming Parquet Handle (OpenAsync/WriteRowGroupAsync/CloseAsync), NestedLevels/ListOf nested-level computer.
   373	- Runtime: native arm64 .NET (AnyCPU 8.0.37) via DOTNET_ROLL_FORWARD; arch -arm64 dotnet for test/convert; mzpeak-validate; python3.11 + pynumpress (test oracle only, Ignored if absent).
   374	- ms-numpress canonical algorithm (Apache-2.0) — vendored as source, ported line-for-line from the reference C++/Java (NOT from RESEARCH-port.md prose).
   375	</dependencies>
