   145	    AUTHORITY: the port is a FAITHFUL LINE-FOR-LINE port of the CANONICAL ms-numpress reference source
   146	    (C++ MSNumpress.cpp / Java MSNumpress.java) for optimalLinearFixedPoint, encodeInt, decodeInt, encodeLinear,
